# Financial & Operational Analysis Steps

## Data Preparation
- Collected and structured simulated financial and operational data
- Verified data accuracy and consistency
- Categorized expenses by department and month

## Analysis Performed
- Budget vs Actual comparison
- Variance analysis to identify overspending and savings
- KPI trend analysis to evaluate departmental performance
- Month-over-month financial trend analysis

## Reporting
- Summarized findings into management-friendly insights
- Prepared data for dashboard visualization and executive review
